  "about_page_title": "About Monologed",
  "about_page_description": "Hi there! 👋\nWe're a team that sees watching movies and TV shows not just as a habit, but as a way of life.\nMonologed was born not just to remember what you've watched, but to feel it, share it, and relive it.\nWe love platforms like Letterboxd and IMDb — but we wanted something that felt a little more like us. More genuine, more personal, more social.\nThat's why Monologed exists.\nHere, you can log what you watch, rate it, write your thoughts, dive into movie and series conversations with friends, and even get inspired when you don't know what to watch next.\nOur only goal is to make sure that a scene you've watched, a line you've heard, or a moment you've felt doesn't just fade away.\nBecause we believe every story you watch has its own monologue.\nAnd we want to capture those monologues — with you.\nWelcome to Monologed.",
  "about_page_features_title": "Features:",
  "about_page_feature_log": "Log movies and TV shows (including specific seasons/episodes).",
  "about_page_feature_rate": "Rate and review content.",
